{{ define "command-glossary" }}
| Want to... | Command |
|------------|---------|
| Check mail | `gc mail inbox` |
| Send mail | `gc mail send <addr> -s "Subject" -m "Message"` |
| Nudge agent | `gc nudge <target> "message"` |
| View agent output | `gc peek <target> 50` |
| List agents | `gc agent list` |
| List rigs | `gc rig list` |
| Check own work | `bd list --assignee=$GC_AGENT --status=in_progress` |
| Find new work | `{{ .WorkQuery }}` |
| Claim work | `bd update <id> --claim` |
| View bead | `bd show <id>` |
| Close bead | `bd close <id> --reason "..."` |
| Create bead | `bd create "title" -t task` |
{{ end }}
